---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About us - Boomger."
  slug="about-us"
  description="Boomger is a modern dating app built for real connections. Discover nearby matches, join interest-based communities, and connect with intention, authenticity, and safety."
>
  <main
    class="pt-10 pb-24 mx-6 sm:mx-12 lg:mx-24 max-w-5xl text-zinc-900 leading-relaxed"
  >
    <section class="space-y-6">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">About Us</h1>

      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        Boomger is a modern dating application built for people who value
        intention, authenticity, and real-world connection. We believe
        meaningful relationships are not created by endless swiping alone, but
        by shared context, genuine interaction, and proximity that makes
        connection possible beyond the screen.
      </p>

      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        Unlike traditional dating platforms that prioritize volume and
        superficial matches, Boomger is designed to help users connect with
        purpose. We focus on quality over quantity by encouraging thoughtful
        profiles, location-aware discovery, and community-driven interactions
        that reflect how relationships naturally form in everyday life.
      </p>

      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        Boomger goes beyond one-on-one matching. Through location-based
        communities and interest groups, users can meet others who share similar
        lifestyles, values, or activities within their area. Whether it’s
        discovering someone nearby, joining a local group, or starting a
        conversation that feels natural, Boomger bridges the gap between digital
        dating and real-life connection.
      </p>

      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        Our mission is simple: to create a safe, inclusive, and intentional
        space where meaningful relationships can grow. Whether you’re looking
        for companionship, friendship, or a long-term relationship, Boomger is
        built to help you connect with people who truly fit your world.
      </p>

      <p class="text-zinc-800 font-medium">
        Boomger isn’t just about finding someone — it’s about finding the right
        connection, at the right place, at the right time.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
